--- h1
How To Create Documentation For A Class
---

--- h2
Simple Method
---

In your class directory, create a file named:

--- pre
<className>_CBDocumentation_description.cbmessage
---


--- h2
Custom Method
---

Implement the (CBAdmin_CBDocumentationForClass_render\(\) (code)) interface on
your class and render whatever you want. You can render views or use
(CBHTMLOutput (code)) functions to include classes, CSS, or JavaScript files.
